<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Post View - Blog Hill</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f0f0; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh;">

    <!-- Post View Section -->
    <div
        style="background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); width: 600px;">
        <!-- Post Title -->
        <h1 style="color: #333;">Post Title</h1>

        <!-- Post Author -->
        <p style="color: #555;">by <strong>Author Name</strong></p>

        <!-- Post Content -->
        <div style="margin-top: 20px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum vel urna felis. Aenean sit amet ex ac
                velit fermentum fermentum. Aliquam erat volutpat.</p>
            <p>Cras dapibus, justo sit amet vehicula viverra, lacus est fermentum nunc, et vehicula leo mi ac nisi. In
                hac habitasse platea dictumst. Curabitur imperdiet ligula at lacinia pretium.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Edit and Delete Buttons -->
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <a href="/edit-post" style="text-decoration: none;">
                <button
                    style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer;">Edit</button>
            </a>
            <form action="/delete-post" method="POST" style="margin: 0;">
                <button type="submit"
                    style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #dc3545; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer;">Delete</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>